results.name: The smallest values m such that A049820(x) = m has exactly n solutions.
comment: The 11 numbers x for which A049820(x) is equal to a(11) are a(11) + {12, 16, 24, 32, 36, 40, 56, 80, 96, 128, 512}. - _Giovanni Resta_, Feb 10 2014
example: For n=4: 22 is the smallest identical value of A049820(x) for 4 distinct numbers x: 25, 26, 28, 30.
